summary: Adds Items like Greybeard Robe in front of Riverwood
descriptionHtml:
Hello Guys,
This is my first Skyrim Mod, it adds Items at Riverwood (Look at the Pictures)
Following Items are added:
-Dremora Gloves, Helmet, Armor, Boots (It says Daedric Armor but its the Dremora Armor)
-Greybeard Robe, Hats, etc.
-Giant Club
-Daedric Artefacts like Volendrung, Sanguines Rose, Molag Bals Mace, Helmet of Clavicus Vile
-Executioner Armor, Mask, Axe, Boots
-Wolf-Armor
-And a lot more!

READ README AND ENJOY! :)
-Vopez
author: Vopez
